      "Title": "Wolfgang.Extensions.Logging.Data.EntityFramework6.EntityFramework6Logging",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Wolfgang.Extensions.Logging.Data.EntityFramework6.EntityFramework6Logging.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">One-call registration of passive EF6 logging. Calling <code>AddLoggingInterceptors</code>\nonce at startup wires command, connection, and transaction interceptors into the\nprocess-global EF6 interception pipeline, so every <code>DbContext</code> in the process\nlogs its activity with no per-query call sites.</p>\n"
    },
